WEBVTT

00:00:00.121 --> 00:00:03.499
Have you ever reached the end
of what feels like a grueling workday

00:00:03.499 --> 00:00:06.502
only to realize you didn’t actually
accomplish anything?

00:00:06.502 --> 00:00:08.337
That it was just meeting after meeting

00:00:08.337 --> 00:00:10.465
after meeting after meeting
after meeting --

00:00:10.465 --> 00:00:12.759
[The Way We Work]

00:00:12.759 --> 00:00:14.260
(Music)

00:00:15.219 --> 00:00:16.971
As a recovering corporate executive,

00:00:16.971 --> 00:00:19.682
I know we all feel
like our time isn’t our own,

00:00:19.682 --> 00:00:21.934
like other people 
are controlling our calendars

00:00:21.934 --> 00:00:23.895
and we’re simply reacting to their whims.

00:00:23.895 --> 00:00:25.938
But calendar creep isn’t inevitable.

00:00:26.314 --> 00:00:28.483
There's so much in the world
we can't control.

00:00:28.483 --> 00:00:30.234
We can’t control our senior leaders,